19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_openpgpkey(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21
22 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
23
24 UNUSED(type);
25 UNUSED(rdclass);
26 UNUSED(callbacks);
27 UNUSED(options);
28 UNUSED(origin);
29
30 /*
31 * Keyring.
32 */
33 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
34}
35
36static inline isc_result_t
37totext_openpgpkey(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
38 isc_region_t sr;
39
40 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
41 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
42
43 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
44
45 /*
46 * Keyring
47 */
48 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
49 RETERR(str_totext("( ", target));
50
51 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_NOCRYPTO) == 0) {
52 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
53 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
54 else
55 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
56 tctx->linebreak, target));
57 } else
58 RETERR(str_totext("[omitted]", target));
59
60 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
61 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
62
63 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
64}
65
66static inline isc_result_t
67fromwire_openpgpkey(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
68 isc_region_t sr;
69
70 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
71
72 UNUSED(type);
73 UNUSED(rdclass);
74 UNUSED(dctx);
75 UNUSED(options);
76
77 /*
78 * Keyring.
79 */
80 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
81 if (sr.length < 1)
82 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
83 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
84 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
85}
86
87static inline isc_result_t
88towire_openpgpkey(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
89 isc_region_t sr;
90
91 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
92 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
93
94 UNUSED(cctx);
95
96 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
97 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
98}

100static inline int
101compare_openpgpkey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
102 isc_region_t r1;
103 isc_region_t r2;
104
105 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
106 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
107 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
108 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
109 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
110
111 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
112 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
113 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
114}
115
116static inline isc_result_t
117fromstruct_openpgpkey(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
118 dns_rdata_openpgpkey_t *sig = source;
119
120 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
121 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
122 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdtype == type);
123 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdclass == rdclass);
124 REQUIRE(sig->keyring != NULL && sig->length != 0);
125
126 UNUSED(type);
127 UNUSED(rdclass);
128
129 /*
130 * Keyring.
131 */
132 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sig->keyring, sig->length));
133}
134
135static inline isc_result_t
136tostruct_openpgpkey(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
137 isc_region_t sr;
138 dns_rdata_openpgpkey_t *sig = target;
139
140 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
141 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
142 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
143
144 sig->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
145 sig->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
146 ISC_LINK_INIT(&sig->common, link);
147
148 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
149
150 /*
151 * Keyring.
152 */
153 sig->length = sr.length;
154 sig->keyring = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, sig->length);
155 if (sig->keyring == NULL)
156 goto cleanup;
157
158 sig->mctx = mctx;
159 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
160
161 cleanup:
162 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
163}
164
165static inline void
166freestruct_openpgpkey(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
167 dns_rdata_openpgpkey_t *sig = (dns_rdata_openpgpkey_t *) source;
168
169 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
170 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
171
172 if (sig->mctx == NULL)
173 return;
174
175 if (sig->keyring != NULL)
176 isc_mem_free(sig->mctx, sig->keyring);
177 sig->mctx = NULL;
178}

191static inline isc_result_t
192digest_openpgpkey(ARGS_DIGEST) {
193 isc_region_t r;
194
195 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_openpgpkey);
196
197 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
198
199 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
200}
